                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8476" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0249</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1384 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">益海嘉里：聚焦ESG实践，探索可持续发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yihai Kerry: Focus on ESG practice and explore the road to sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邱卫林,彭笑微</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">益海嘉里金龙鱼粮油食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；可持续发展；公司治理；企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG; Sustainable development; Corporate governance; Corporate social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国政府一直对农产品和食品加工企业的可持续发展非常重视，出台了一系列政策，旨在推动农产品和食品加工企业的可持续发展，并出台了相关的ESG政策，以提高行业的整体竞争力和可持续性。作为中国重要的农产品和食品加工企业，本案例以益海嘉里金龙鱼粮油食品股份有限公司为样本，深入剖析了该公司如何将ESG理念融入公司发展战略，并通过实施ESG策略，如加强环境管理、提升企业社会责任和提高公司治理水平等措施，有效解决了公司发展中的关键问题。公司注重ESG信息披露的透明度，定期发布ESG报告，展示了在环境保护、社会责任和公司治理方面的努力和成果，不仅提升了公司的信誉度和品牌价值，也为同行业提供了宝贵的管理经验。本案例在帮助学生了解ESG信息披露的同时也可以引导我国企业通过实施ESG实现企业社会责任。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The Chinese government has always attached great importance to the sustainable development of agricultural products and food processing enterprises, and has introduced a series of policies aimed at promoting the sustainable development of agricultural products and food processing enterprises, and has introduced relevant ESG policies to improve the overall competitiveness and sustainability of the industry. As an important agricultural products and food processing enterprise in China, this case takes Yihai Kerry Golden Dragon Fish Grain, Oil and Food Co., Ltd. as a sample to deeply analyze how the company integrates ESG concepts into its development strategy, and implements ESG strategies, such as strengthening environmental management, enhancing corporate social responsibility and improving corporate governance. Effectively solve the key problems in the development of the company. The company attaches great importance to the transparency of ESG information disclosure, and regularly releases ESG reports, showing the efforts and achievements in environmental protection, social responsibility and corporate governance, which not only enhances the company&#39;s credibility and brand value, but also provides valuable management experience for the industry. This case not only helps students understand ESG information disclosure, but also guides Chinese enterprises to realize corporate social responsibility through the implementation of ESG.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG概念内涵；ESG驱动因素；ESG作用机制；可持续发展理论；ESG信息披露；ESG企业价值；企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-08</td>
                            </tr>
